---
title: "Services — Slade Networks"
description: "Wi-Fi, cameras, VoIP phones, cabling, and ongoing support — professional UniFi installation for homes and small businesses in the Finger Lakes, NY."
navActive: services
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block pageStyles %}
  <style>
    .section { padding: 24px 0 56px }
    .supportSection { padding: 0 0 56px }

    /* Primary service cards */
    .primaryGrid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .primaryCard {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      padding: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      transition: transform .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease);
    }
    .primaryCard:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
      border-color: var(--primary-100);
    }

    .primaryCard h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }

    .primaryCard p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .primaryCard .media {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 80px;
    }

    .primaryCard .media img {
      width: 55%;
      max-width: 200px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      object-fit: contain;
      transition: transform .3s var(--ease);
    }

    .primaryCard:hover .media img {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Divider */
    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      margin: 36px 0 28px;
    }

    /* Secondary service cards */
    .secondaryGrid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .secondaryCard {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: var(--r-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-xs);
      padding: 20px;
      transition: transform .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease);
    }
    .secondaryCard:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      border-color: var(--primary-100);
    }

    .secondaryCard h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }

    .secondaryCard p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Pricing note */
    .pricingNote {
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: var(--r-lg);
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .pricingNote strong { color: var(--gray-900) }
    .pricingNote a { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600 }

    /* Support card */
    .supportCard {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(37,99,235,.03) 0%, rgba(37,99,235,.06) 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary-200);
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .supportBadge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      background: var(--primary-100);
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .07em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: var(--r-sm);
      padding: 5px 10px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .supportCard h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .supportCard > p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      max-width: 82ch;
    }
    .supportCard > p + p { margin-top: 10px }

    .supportFooter {
      margin-top: 22px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .supportFooter .processLink {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .ctaSection { padding: 0 0 72px }

    @media(max-width:980px) {
      .primaryGrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr }
      .secondaryGrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr }
    }
    @media(max-width:700px) {
      .primaryGrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr }
    }
    @media(max-width:480px) {
      .secondaryGrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr }
    }
  </style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="heroBadge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v4m0 14v4M4.22 4.22l2.83 2.83m9.9 9.9 2.83 2.83M1 12h4m14 0h4M4.22 19.78l2.83-2.83m9.9-9.9 2.83-2.83"/></svg>
          Full-service installs
        </div>
        <h1>Everything Your Network Needs</h1>
        <p class="subtext">
          From planning to installation to ongoing support — we handle Wi-Fi, cameras, phones, and the infrastructure behind them so your network just works.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sectionLabel">Core services</p>
        <div class="primaryGrid reveal-stagger">

          <article class="primaryCard">
            <h3>Wi-Fi</h3>
            <p>Access points planned for your layout, installed cleanly, and verified for coverage in every room — living areas, offices, patios. No dead spots, no guessing.</p>
            <div class="media">
              <img src="/assets/u7-pro-xg-2.png" alt="UniFi Wi-Fi access point" loading="lazy">
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="primaryCard">
            <h3>Cameras</h3>
            <p>Strategic placement, no blind spots, and footage accessible from your phone. We confirm angles, recording, and remote playback before we leave.</p>
            <div class="media">
              <img src="/assets/uvc-g6-pro-turret-10.png" alt="UniFi security camera" loading="lazy">
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="primaryCard">
            <h3>VoIP Phones</h3>
            <p>Business phone systems on UniFi Talk — number porting handled, clean cutover, and tested end-to-end. Calls are clear, phones just work.</p>
            <div class="media">
              <img src="/assets/utp-g3-touch-enterprise-1.png" alt="UniFi Talk desk phone" loading="lazy">
            </div>
          </article>

        </div>

        <hr class="divider">

        <p class="sectionLabel">Infrastructure</p>
        <div class="secondaryGrid reveal-stagger">

          <article class="secondaryCard">
            <h3>Structured cabling</h3>
            <p>Clean Ethernet runs, labeled jacks, and neat wall plates — built right so future changes are easy.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="secondaryCard">
            <h3>Gateways and switching</h3>
            <p>Right-sized routing and switching gear, installed cleanly for stable performance as your network grows.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="secondaryCard">
            <h3>Racks and mounting</h3>
            <p>Equipment mounted and patched properly — organized cables, labeled ports, easy to service later.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="secondaryCard">
            <h3>Power and failover</h3>
            <p>Battery backup for critical gear and cellular failover so a downed ISP connection doesn't take everything offline.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="secondaryCard">
            <h3>Network storage</h3>
            <p>Centralized file access and camera recordings — available to the right people, properly backed up.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="secondaryCard">
            <h3>Display and casting</h3>
            <p>Digital signage and wireless casting that stays connected and is simple to manage day-to-day.</p>
          </article>

        </div>

        <div class="pricingNote reveal">
          <strong>No surprises on pricing.</strong> Every project begins with a free on-site consultation and a written, itemized quote — you'll know exactly what's included before any work starts. <a href="/process/">See how the process works &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="supportSection reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="supportCard">
          <div class="supportBadge">Recommended add-on</div>
          <h2>Ongoing Support Plan</h2>
          <p>Most issues after an install don't need a truck roll — they need someone who knows the system and can resolve things fast. We monitor your network, handle firmware updates proactively, and troubleshoot remotely so problems get fixed before they disrupt your day.</p>
          <p>Especially valuable for businesses where downtime has a real cost.</p>
          <ul class="benefitList" aria-label="Support plan benefits">
            <li>Remote monitoring</li>
            <li>Proactive firmware updates</li>
            <li>Remote troubleshooting</li>
            <li>Priority response times</li>
            <li>Most issues fixed without a site visit</li>
            <li>One point of contact for anything network</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="supportFooter">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">Ask about support plans</a>
            <a class="processLink" href="/process/">How the full process works &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ctaSection reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="ctaInner">
          <div>
            <h2>Not sure what you need?</h2>
            <p>That's what the consultation is for. We'll visit your space, understand the problem, and recommend the right solution — free, with no obligation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ctaButtons">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">Book a free consultation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
{% endblock %}
